  "title": "Site Engineer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p><ul><li>Liaise with sub-contractors on day-to-day site operations.</li><li>Proactively manage any changes in project scope.</li><li>Identify and resolve any site issues with other trades.</li><li>Ensure the project meets clients' quality standards.</li><li>Able to interact with all levels of stakeholders.</li><li>Attend regular consultant meeting</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Degree in Civil Engineering recognised by the Professional Engineer Board (PEB) / Building Construction Authority (BCA) is a must</li><li>Min 5 years of local working experience.</li><li>Good computer literacy.</li><li>Self-motivated and able to work independently.</li><li>Alternate Saturday work</li></ul>",
