    "description": "<p>Since its establishment in 1984, Kwan Yong Construction has grown into a company known for delivering award-winning construction projects across the public, commercial and private sectors. Our focus is to become a progressive organization whilst seeking growth opportunities and rising up to challenges.&nbsp;We foster strong relationships with our stakeholders to ensure that efficient and effective systems are put in place to achieve the best outcomes for the project. At Kwan Yong, our teams demonstrate professionalism, leadership,&nbsp;problem solving skills and most importantly, we are not locked into the old paradigm. Our focus on intelligent and competitive delivery, twinned with resources gives us the edge and ability to deliver work with passion and innovation.</p>",
